Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ubehlo už pol roka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.58,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... od kedy An-chan umrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále sa to ťažko prijíma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:45.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som šťastný...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:49.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... že sme sa s An-chanom stretli.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol som šťastný.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože...{\alphaFF} sme sa vtedy s An-chanom nestretli...
